flowchart TB
    BR[Confirmed business rule] --> DM[Data model and status transitions]
    DM --> API[Backend use case and API]
    API --> UI[Phone-first role interface]
    API --> JOB[Background job / integration adapter]
    API --> AUDIT[Audit record]
    UI --> TEST[Acceptance test with real Maetore data]
    JOB --> TEST
    AUDIT --> TEST
    TEST -->|Pass| RELEASE[Release behind feature flag]
    TEST -->|Fail| FIX[Fix the same slice]
    FIX --> DM

    subgraph RULE[Delivery rule]
      R1[Finish one usable business workflow end-to-end]
      R2[Do not build disconnected tables or screens]
      R3[Old system stays available until parity is proven]
    end
